    "ragtruth_id": "288",
    "text": "Cynthia Lennon, the first wife of John Lennon and mother of Julian Lennon, died on Wednesday 1st April following a short but brave battle with cancer. Her son, Julian, announced the news on his website, stating that she passed away at her home in Mallorca, Spain. Cynthia Lennon was 75. John and Cynthia met at art school and were married for six years, from 1962 to 1968. The couple divorced in 1968, by which time John was in a relationship with Yoko Ono. Cynthia Lennon married three more times after John and wrote two books about her marriage to the Beatle, \"A Twist of Lennon\" and \"John.\"",
