    "text": "Cynthia Lennon, the first wife of John Lennon and mother of Julian Lennon, has died at the age of 75 after a brief battle with cancer. She was a stabilizing force for John during his rise to fame with the Beatles, but their marriage ended in divorce in 1968. Despite the challenges of fame and her husband's infidelities, Cynthia remained loyal to John and wrote two books about their marriage. She is survived by her son Julian and her fourth husband Noel Charles, who passed away in 2013.",
